high_descs: Pick up the loaf of bread from the coffee table.
Turn around and head straight to the fridge in the kitchen area.
Place the loaf of bread in the fridge, let it cool, then remove it.
Turn to the countertop to the left of the fridge.
Place the loaf of bread on the countertop next to the microwave.

Put the bread on the countertop between the microwave and the refrigerator.
